Plain-language summary (NOT a substitute for the canonical and full
text below)
============================================================================

  - You may use, copy, modify, and share this software AT NO COST if
    BOTH of the following are true:
      (i)  Your total staff (employees and independent contractors,
           combined, at any point in the calendar year) is no more
           than ONE (1) person; AND
      (ii) Your annual revenue, from all sources combined, does not
           exceed THIRTY THOUSAND US DOLLARS ($30,000 USD) per
           calendar year.

  - This is a much narrower grant than the standard PolyForm Small
    Business thresholds (100 people / $1,000,000 USD revenue). The
    canonical PolyForm Small Business text below applies, and the
    Additional Restriction below tightens its thresholds.

  - Any use that does NOT meet both conditions above requires a
    separate paid license from the rights holder.

  - The software is provided "AS IS", without any warranty. The
    licensor is not liable for any damages related to the software or
    these terms.

  - All notices (copyright, license, source line) must be preserved
    in redistributions.

If the summary and the canonical text differ, the canonical text
below (as narrowed by the Additional Restriction) controls.

